  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ant
    An ant who starts from the beginning of the maze and through it to the end.
    EnergyPlant
    A version of a plant that shoots a beam of energy at any insect that is nearby.
    Fruit
    A fruit that is at the end of the maze created by the player The insects try to get to the fruit and if they do and eat it completely, the game ends
    Insect
    An insect who starts from the beginning of the maze and goes to the end.
    Plant
    A plant that attacks any insect that is nearby.
    Wall
    A wall that blocks ants and plants can be placed on this.
